[30;1m48 | [0m[35m            data to an Existing Experiment or to control the key of new experiments (for example to [0m
[30;1m49 | [0m[35m            identifier). Must be an alphanumeric string whose length is between 32 and 50 characters[0m
[30;1m50 | [0m[35m        mode (str, optional): Control how the Comet experiment is started.[0m
[30;1m51 | [0m[35m[0m

[30;1m79 | [0m[35m            # call as the call might fail and the last beat would not been[0m
[30;1m80 | [0m[35m            # updated. That would trigger a heartbeat for each message.[0m
[30;1m81 | [0m[35m            self.last_beat = time.time()[0m
